---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Our Solutions — PerfEco Consulting" description="6 intervention areas: organisational diagnostic, performance management, process optimisation, digital transformation, executive support, skills transfer.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-16">

    <section class="bg-navy-dark text-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Our solutions</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Concrete results for every function</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our interventions cover the full spectrum of organisational performance — from financial visibility to pragmatic digital transformation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">01</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Organisational diagnostic</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">CEO / CFO / COO</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">PerfEco analyses how your organisation really works before making any recommendation.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Mapping of real processes</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Identification of blockers and approval circuits</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Role and responsibility analysis</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Identification of duplication and wasted time</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Assessment of reporting quality</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">02</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Performance management</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">CEO / CFO</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Build reliable management reporting for the executive committee — based on facts, not intuitions.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Useful, actionable KPIs</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Executive committee dashboards</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Cash flow, margin, cost and lead time reporting</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Multi-entity data consolidation</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Reporting automation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">03</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Process optimisation</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">COO / Operations</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Simplify processes without destabilising the organisation. Reduce the friction that slows everything down.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Removal of unnecessary steps</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Clarification of approval thresholds</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Better distribution of responsibilities</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Reduction of delays and lead times</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Improved cross-departmental coordination</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">04</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Pragmatic digital transformation</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">CIO / CEO</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Digital technology in service of the organisation — not the other way around. Tools adapted to the local context.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Reporting automation</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>ERP / CRM / business tools</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Power BI and dashboards</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>IT governance and security</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Rationalisation of existing tools</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">05</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Executive support</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">CEO / CFO / COO / CIO</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">PerfEco speaks the language of executives. Summaries, briefings, decision papers — directly actionable.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Preparation of strategic meetings</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Executive committee papers</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Action plans and opportunity matrices</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Executive summaries</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Structuring of executive decisions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0"><div class="text-5xl font-bold text-teal/20">06</div></div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Training and skills transfer</h2>
              <span class="text-xs bg-teal/10 text-teal font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Leadership teams</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">PerfEco does not aim to create dependency. The goal is to transfer methods and make teams more autonomous.</p>
            <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Training in PerfEco methods</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Working alongside existing teams</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Building lasting practices</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Progressive team autonomy</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600"><span class="text-teal mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>Post-assignment follow-up</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-14">
        <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-teal hover:bg-teal-dark text-white font-bold px-6 py-3.5 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow text-lg">
          Discuss your situation
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
